title: Statement by the President on Romanian National Day | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
December 01, 2009

 



Statement by the President on Romanian National Day




I send my best wishes to all those who will celebrate Romanian National Day.  Our nations share nearly 130 years of relations, and Romania remains a close ally and partner as we face the challenges of the world.  I especially offer my congratulations to the Romanian-American community that are observing this occasion.
